solution:
**Before:** `request.getHeaders().addIfAbsent(headerName, value);`

**After:**
```java
if (!request.getHeaders().containsHeader(headerName)) {
  request.getHeaders().add(headerName, value);
}
```

**Why:** In Spring Framework 7, HttpHeaders no longer implements MultiValueMap, so addIfAbsent() (inherited from MultiValueMap) is gone. Use containsHeader() + add() for equivalent behavior.
